data.value: To analyse collected data please click the button below and it will redirect you to VTS Automonitoring system where you will be able to upload your data for analysis. Click "Help" button to see the VTS Automonitoring system usage help.

data.name: AboutTextContent
data.value: VTS Agent application is a part of the VTS Avtomonitoring software package. It's completely free. Please visit our website Vtsautomonitoring.com to download the latest version or to learn more about the VTS Avtomonitoring vehicle health monitoring system.

data.name: DataExportWindowTextExplanation
data.value: The data has been exported to a .vts file. It is required in order to upload it to the VTS Monitor web application where diagnostic data from the file will be stored in the central database of the system, and analyzed. Should we go to the VTS Monitor web page to upload the file?

data.value: Could not find any data captured from a vehicle by Lexia, PP2000 or DiagBox diagnostic system on this computer.

data.name: UnrecognizedDataExplanatoryText

data.name: UnrecognizedDataButtonTooltipText
data.value: Unrecognized data found. Press to process it.

data.name: NewVersionExplanatoryText
data.value: It's better than current and is free as well. We recommend you to download it now or later from our website.

data.name: NoConnectionExplanatoryText
data.value: You need network connection to log on or register. Loggong on with a user account allows you to enable all application's abilities for your car parameters monitoring.
